Welcome to my Django-Project.
Service which anables users to add surfspots and write reviews about them as well as an admin panel.

The project includes also diverse tests

To start the app:

1. in terminal run: : 
    $pipenv install django
to create a virtual environment and install django

2. in terminal run: 
    $pipenv shell

to start the Virtualenv

If you are uisng VS-Code:

3. set up interpreter:
    1. open comand palette  (cmd + shift + P)
    2. type select interpreter
    3. enter interpreter path
    4. in terminal run 'pipenv --env' copy Virtualenv location from terminal appending    /bin/python  in the end

4. run
    $python manage.py runserver




to run all the tests:

$python manage.py test spots